# Concept: dicts (dictionaries)
# A dict stores named values. Read and write fields using dot notation.
# Run it with: atena run 09-dicts.atena

# Create a dict with two fields
person = {name = "Ana", age = 20}

# Read a value using dot notation
show person.name

# Update a value using dot notation
person.age = 21
show "Updated age: " + person.age
